            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p xml:lang="heb">תתניח נפשה דחלפו<lb/>ברתה <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="5"/> דמיתת<lb/>ביום תלתה בחדעשר<lb/>יומין בירח אלול בשת<supplied reason="omitted">ה</supplied>
               <lb/>דשמטתה דהיא שנת<lb/>ארבע מיה
                    ותלתין<lb/>וחמש שנין לחרבן<lb/>בית מקדשה שלום<lb/>אל ישראל שלום</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Rested be the soul of Ḥalifu<lb/>daughter ....., who died<lb/>on the third day
                    (Tuesday), on the eleventh<lb/>day of the month Elul, in the Sabbatical year,
                    which is the year<lb/>four hundred and thirty<lb break="no"/>five years of the
                    destruction<lb/>of the Santuary. Peace<lb/>upon Israel, peace.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>Since it is less likely to have a mistake in the indication of the sabbatical
                    year, the error may have occurred with the era year (435 instead of 434),
                    probably due to the month Elul, which precedes the start of the new year in
                    Tishri.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
